data.description: Price reduced for a quick sale! This acreage is tucked away just off of Highway 14 approximately 2 miles north of Chariton.  Offering a Morton Building 4-bedroom home, 3+ car detached garage, sheds, this is one you won't want to miss.  Large kitchen with center island is open to the dining and living room, with two bedrooms and a bathroom on each end of the home. Washer and dryer are in the full bathroom while the 3/4 bathroom is attached to the master bedroom along with a walk-in closet. Large covered deck on the back of the home and small deck on the front for enjoying your little piece of paradise!
